git clone https://github.com/GlobalReconReport/WebWeaver.git
cd WebWeaver
sudo bash install.sh

The only thing to sort is the mitmproxy CA cert — just run this once:
mitmdump &
sleep 3
pkill mitmdump
sudo cp ~/.mitmproxy/mitmproxy-ca-cert.pem /usr/local/share/ca-certificates/mitmproxy.crt
sudo update-ca-certificates
